## 9. Common Mistakes & Key Takeaways

| Mistake | Fix |
|---------|-----|
| Ignoring context | Use LLM for ambiguous mappings |
| One direction only | Build bidirectional mappings |

| # | Takeaway |
|---|----------|
| 1 | **Rule-based** is fast but misses context |
| 2 | **LLMs** handle multi-script transliteration zero-shot |
| 3 | **Longest-match-first** improves rule-based quality |
| 4 | **Script detection** enables automatic routing |

